10,"Joe Hunter Memorial Drill ","joe-hunter-memorial-drill-","

Thursday, July 3rd, Joe Hunter Memorial Drill at Hempstead, Drill Time 6:00pm.

Help honor one of New York's Bravest.  Joe Hunter was a member of the South Hempstead Rascals and FDNY who was killed in the Sept. 11th attacks. The drill was started in 2003 with the top ten finishers of the previous year's state drill invited to attend.
